  "meal_prep_notes": "The batter keeps 3 days in the fridge; stir gently before reuse. Cooked dosas reheat best on a dry pan over low heat for 1 minute per side. For batch cooking, ferment the batter in one container and portion toppings separately so later rounds stay crisp.",
